<br><br>With the rise of technology, particularly social media and online platforms, social learning has become more accessible and inclusive than ever before. Platforms like LinkedIn Learning, Coursera, and Khan Academy provide opportunities for learners to connect with experts, join communities, and collaborate on projects.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-135_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-136_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-137_ pf-heading-1-h3">The benefits of social learning
