</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-147_ pf-text-1"><b>Deeper understanding</b> -&nbsp;Through interactions with peers and mentors, learners gain new perspectives, insights, and approaches to problem-solving. This diversity of thought enriches the learning experience and promotes critical thinking and creativity.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-149_ pf-text-1"><b>Skill development</b> - Social learning provides opportunities for skill development through practice, feedback, and collaboration. Whether it's mastering a new language, honing technical skills, or refining leadership abilities, learners can benefit from the expertise and support of their peers.
